# Styling and Components Guide

The project uses Element Plus for UI components with custom styling and animations.

## Global Styles

[style.css](mdc:src/style.css) contains:
- Color variables
- Typography settings
- Animation keyframes
- Utility classes
- Layout primitives

## Theme System

1. Color Scheme
   - Dark theme with gradient backgrounds
   - Accent colors for interactions
   - Emotion-based color feedback
   - Accessibility-friendly contrast

2. Typography
   - Noto Serif SC for traditional text
   - System fonts for UI elements
   - Responsive font sizing
   - Line height optimization

## Component Library

1. Ancestor Components
   - Avatar display
   - Trait tags
   - Evolution progress
   - Emotion indicators

2. Interaction Components
   - Offering buttons
   - Cooldown indicators
   - Affection meter
   - Quote bubbles

3. Game Components
   - Quiz cards
   - Red packet animations
   - Progress indicators
   - Result displays

4. Share Components
   - Template cards
   - Preview frames
   - Social buttons
   - Image generators

## Animation System

1. Micro-interactions
   - Button hover effects
   - State transitions
   - Loading indicators
   - Error feedback

2. Major Animations
   - Page transitions
   - Quote typing effect
   - Evolution celebrations
   - Share card generation

## Responsive Design

- Mobile-first approach
- Breakpoint system
- Flexible layouts
- Touch-friendly interactions
